      "content": "i don't know if i want to wait for the sun to rise. it just feels like i'm exhausted from fighting it. sometimes i just think about how much easier it would be if i didn't have to wake up to this emptiness every single morning. like, if i could just stop the noise and the pain for good. does that even make sense?",
